These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
City: hamburg, venice, london, edinburgh
Flower: iris, orchid, daisy, begonia
1. City:london is between Flower:daisy and Flower:orchid##2
2. City:edinburgh is on the left or right of Flower:daisy##3
3. Flower:daisy is not to the left of Flower:daisy##8
4. Flower:orchid != City:london##6
5. City:london is somewhere to the right of City:hamburg##5
6. City:hamburg is on the right of Flower:iris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | edinburgh  | hamburg | london | venice  |
| Flower   | iris | daisy   | begonia  | orchid |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Transport: van, bus, scooter, roller
City: boston, nizza, miami, liverpool
1. City:liverpool is not to the left of City:liverpool##8
2. Transport:van is somewhere to the right of Transport:roller##5
3. Transport:van == City:nizza##1
4. Transport:roller is between Transport:van and Transport:bus##2
5. Transport:bus is somewhere between Transport:scooter and City:boston##7
6. City:miami is somewhere to the left of Transport:bus##5
7. City:boston is not to the left of City:boston##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Transport   | scooter | bus          | roller | van     |
| City    | miami      | liverpool | boston | nizza |

