.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Game: backgammon, whist, bridge, monopoly
Color: lavender, purple, coral, aquamarine
1. Color:lavender is not to the left of Game:bridge##8
2. Color:purple is on the far left##1
3. Game:whist is on the right of Game:backgammon##1
4. Game:whist is in an even position##4
5. Game:monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
6. Game:backgammon is somewhere to the left of Color:aquamarine##5
7. Game:monopoly == Color:coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game           | backgammon | whist | bridge     | monopoly |
| Color   | purple    | aquamarine   | lavender | coral    |

